Ya, Shakti.

00:18:33.400 --> 00:18:35.120
Bawa Dr Shiv ke kamarnya.

00:18:35.680 --> 00:18:36.640
Oke.

00:18:36.760 --> 00:18:38.040
Pergi.  - Ayo berangkat, Shiv.

